1362.name: NiCu30Mn
1362.Applications: Shipbuilding, seawater evaporation plants, tubes, pump building, offshore etc. NiCu30Mn is suitable for dissimilar welding between Nickel 200-201, stainless steel, carbon steel, Inconel and Incoloy alloys, Nickel Copper and Copper nickel alloys.
1362.Suitable_For: 2.4360, 2.4375, NiCu30Fe, NiCu30Al, Monel 400, R405, alloy K500 and dissimilar welding between these alloys.
